<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">

    <title>Privacy</title>

    <style type="text/css">
        html, body, div, span, applet, object, iframe,
        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, p, blockquote, pre,
        a, abbr, acronym, address, big, cite, code,
        del, dfn, em, img, ins, kbd, q, s, samp,
        small, strike, strong, sub, sup, tt, var,
        center,
        dl, dt, dd,
        fieldset, form, label, legend,
        table, caption, tbody, tfoot, thead, tr, th, td,
        article, aside, canvas, details, embed,
        figure, figcaption, footer, header,
        menu, nav, output, ruby, section, summary,
        time, mark, audio, video {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
            vertical-align: baseline;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Gilroy Bold';
            src: url('https://courses.prostoapp.com/fonts/Gilroy-Bold.eot');
            src: url('https://courses.prostoapp.com/fonts/Gilroy-Bold.eot?#iefix') format('embedded-opentype'),
            url('https://courses.prostoapp.com/fonts/Gilroy-Bold.woff') format('woff'),
            url('https://courses.prostoapp.com/fonts/Gilroy-Bold.ttf') format('truetype');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Gotham Pro Regular';
            src: url('https://courses.prostoapp.com/fonts/GothamPro.eot');
            src: url('https://courses.prostoapp.com/fonts/GothamPro.eot?#iefix') format('embedded-opentype'),
            url('https://courses.prostoapp.com/fonts/GothamPro.woff') format('woff'),
            url('https://courses.prostoapp.com/fonts/GothamPro.ttf') format('truetype');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        html, body {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .page {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-family: 'Gotham Pro Regular';
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
        }

        .pageUpperBlock {
            display: flex;
            height: 430px;
            width: 100%;
            flex-direction: row;
        }

        .mainImage {
            position: absolute;
            width: 240px;
            height: 250px;
            left: 80px;
            top: 30px;
            z-index: -3;
        }

        .mainImageBorder {
            position: absolute;
            width: 330px;
            height: 360px;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 3;
        }

        .logo {
            float: right;
            width: 50px;
            margin: 47px 107px 7px 0;
            height: 50px;
        }

        .leftUpperPart {
            display: block;
            float: left;
            width: 50%;
        }

        .rightUpperPart {
            display: flex;
            width: 50%;
            float: right;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer {
            position: fixed;
            left: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            padding: 30px 35%;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .footerText {
            font-family: 'Gilroy Bold';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 15px;
            width: 200px;
            color: #000000;
        }

        .rightUpperPartLogo {
            font-family: 'Arial';;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 14px;
            color: #000000;
            float: right;
            margin: 0 100px 11px 0;
        }

        .rightUpperPartTitle {
            font-family: 'Arial';
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            line-height: 39px;
            color: #AB9E98;
            float: right;
            margin: 0 0 11px 20px;
        }

        .rightUpperPartAdditional {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-family: 'Gotham Pro Regular';
            line-height: 14px;
            color: #000000;
            width: 160px;
            height: 28px;
            float: right;
            margin: 0 50px 0 0;
        }

        .middleBlock {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: -50px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: block;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .middleTitle {
            font-family: 'Arial';
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            line-height: 39px;
            color: #000000;
        }

        .promocode {
            font-family: 'Arial';
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 36px;
            line-height: 56px;
            color: #000000;
        }

        .additionalText {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-family: 'Gotham Pro Regular';
            line-height: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #000000;
            padding: 15px 0;
        }

        .link {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-family: 'Gotham Pro Regular';
            line-height: 14px;
            color: #2fa590;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .rowBlock {
            width: 100%;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .rowPromocodeBlockContainer {
            display: block;
            width: 33%;
            margin-left: -25px;
            float: left;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .rowBlockContainer {
            display: block;
            width: 33%;

            float: left;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .rowLetterBlockContainer {
            display: block;
            width: 33%;
            text-align: center;
            float: left;
        }

        .promocodeImg {
            width: 45px;
            margin-left: 40px;
            height: 32px;
        }

        .phoneImg {
            width: 26px;
            margin-left: 55px;
            height: 42px;
        }

        .letterImg {
            width: 35px;
            margin-left: 60px;
            height: 42px;
        }

        .additionalPromocodeText {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-family: 'Gotham Pro Regular';
            line-height: 14px;
            width: 133px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #000000;
            padding: 15px 0;
            margin-left: 24%;
        }

        .additionalPhoneText {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-family: 'Gotham Pro Regular';
            line-height: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 150px;
            color: #000000;
            padding: 15px 0;
            margin-left: 24%;
        }

        .additionalLetterText {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-family: 'Gotham Pro Regular';
            line-height: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 160px;
            color: #000000;
            padding: 15px 0;
            margin-left: 24%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="page">
    <div class="pageUpperBlock">
        <div class="rightUpperPart">
            <img src="https://sun9-62.userapi.com/1tswt__MyPdVQ2fgBAveUgC6ST80tMMnwVQerw/YrohCZFADZI.jpg" class="logo"/>
            <p class="rightUpperPartLogo">Prosto App</p>
            <p class="rightUpperPartTitle">Подарочный сертификат</p>
            <p class="rightUpperPartAdditional">Вам подарили спокойствие, хороший сон и осознанность</p>
        </div>
        <div class="leftUpperPart">
            <img src="https://i.imgur.com/Q7QuN1F.png" class="mainImage"/>
            <img src="https://i.imgur.com/hjucWtc.png" class="mainImageBorder"/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="middleBlock">
        <p class="middleTitle">Промокод</p>
        <p class="additionalText">Подписка на <%= months %> <%= monthsText %> в подарок</p>
        <p class="promocode"><%= text %></p>
        <p class="additionalText">Активируйте на сайте <a href="https://code.prostoapp.ru/" class="link">code.prostoapp.ru</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="rowBlock">
        <div class="rowPromocodeBlockContainer">
            <img src="https://i.imgur.com/Lk7t97c.png" class="promocodeImg"/>
            <p class="additionalPromocodeText">Зайдите на сайт <a href="https://code.prostoapp.ru/" class="link">code.prostoapp.ru</a> и активируйте промокод</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rowBlockContainer">
            <img src="https://i.imgur.com/BYrjbwX.png" class="phoneImg"/>
            <p class="additionalPhoneText">Укажите на сайте номер телефона, который будете использовать для доступа в приложение</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rowLetterBlockContainer">
            <img src="https://i.imgur.com/7OZO4q9.png" class="letterImg"/>
            <p class="additionalLetterText">Войдите в приложение под указанным номером телефона. Вы увидите сообщение, что вы получили подписку в подарок</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p class="footerText">Медитация — это Просто<p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
